row_list=[]

with open('nycflights.csv',mode='r',encoding='utf-8',newline='') as f:
    data_reader=csv.reader(f,delimiter=',')
    header=next(data_reader)
    print(header)
    for row in data_reader: 
        row_list.append(row)
       # print(row)    
        
len_rows = len(row_list)
print("Tổng số dòng data: ",len_rows)
